The area contained inside the P-V graph of a thermodynamic cycle is equal to which of the following?

choices.W: The change in pressure over one cycle
choices.X: The change in volume over one cycle

choices.Z: The change in internal energy in one cycle

answer: Y) The amount of work done in one cycle

choices.Z: There is not enough information to determine the error
